EnBW CEO Sees Shortages Due to Nuclear Exit, Sueddeutsche Says

-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 
2011-04-15T16:27:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-15/enbw-ceo-sees-shortages-due-to-nuclear-exit-sueddeutsche-says.html
EnBW Energie Baden-Wuerttemberg
AG (EBK) ’s Chief Executive Officer Hans-Peter Villis said further
nuclear reactor closures in  Germany  may lead to “acute
shortages” in power, the  Sueddeutsche Zeitung  reported, citing
an interview.  Germany may see its first serious problems ensuring energy
availability in decades, the newspaper quoted Villis as saying
in a preview of an interview to be published tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Naomi Kresge in Berlin at 
